{"tid":2264670,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[學佛][阿彌陀佛]佈施笑容","createTime":"2020-10-30T22:55:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-31T08:37:09.000Z","uid":347001,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3e44626cccbf61fb6c641b8381d140c85e7faa9f","tid":2264670,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":15,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T22:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6477HN8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6477HN8.jpg&h=6d9f6a7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7629fcceb316237ce773706f0e00815e14f38e6","tid":2264670,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"3e44626cccbf61fb6c641b8381d140c85e7faa9f","tid":2264670,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":15,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T22:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6477HN8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6477HN8.jpg&h=6d9f6a7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T22:55:55.000Z","msg":"&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;分隔線&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n念念不忘阿彌陀佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請善用起底功能 翻看其他智慧經文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"pink\">佛教是教育，不是宗教，教什麼？教我們修清淨心，教我們幸福快樂，教我們健康長壽，過幸福美滿的人生<br />\n<br />\n同時教我們宇宙真相💫<br />\n<br />\n學佛是人生最高的享受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n阿彌陀佛🙏🏻</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">學佛就是將佛陀的教誨落實到日常生活當中</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n小妹的學佛筆記🙏🏻還在努力學習當中🙇🏻&zwj;♀️<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NdvWbzO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNdvWbzO.png&h=b69b0f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rF0mSOt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrF0mSOt.png&h=ca310694&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMATQwD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMATQwD.png&h=4d6eba3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與佛有緣的同修可以在Facebook search 淨空法師/阿彌陀佛/念佛成佛 搜索更多經文+智慧字句<br />\n許多佛菩薩都把經文的精華/重點節錄了出來<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/amituofobuddha/?ref=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Famituofobuddha%2F%3Fref%3Dshare&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=3d31aa60\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/amituofobuddha/?ref=share</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nianAmitabha/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FnianAmitabha%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=8df60c99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nianAmitabha/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kanpofanxia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fkanpofanxia%2F&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=69465fd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kanpofanxia/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"pink\"><span class=\"large\">或在ig 搜索 amitabha_hk</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"pink\">佛說現在是末法時期 淨宗法門成就<br />\n淨宗法門念的是一句「阿彌陀佛」<br />\n看的是一部《無量壽經》</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n文字版看上此網站瀏覽完整版無量壽經<br />\n<a href=\"http://ft.hwadzan.tw/index_as.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fft.hwadzan.tw%2Findex_as.php&d=e7N1rpd9%2BHLCKfTw7%2FjGdqpJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=cfe87ff4\" target=\"_blank\">http://ft.hwadzan.tw/index_as.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPQ9BbL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPQ9BbL.png&h=789fbe22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在經題搜索 02 就係無量壽經<br />\n<br />\n或者也可以上youtube 搜索🔍 淨空法師 無量壽經<br />\n都可以的🙏🏻阿彌陀佛"},{"pid":"93d2273e090fde590d73d0e825b27af511b6afaa","tid":2264670,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e44626cccbf61fb6c641b8381d140c85e7faa9f","tid":2264670,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":15,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T22:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6477HN8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6477HN8.jpg&h=6d9f6a7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T22:56:06.000Z","msg":"阿彌陀佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43f5e651ba48707c839e1c473d1a1de2d1a49e0","tid":2264670,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e44626cccbf61fb6c641b8381d140c85e7faa9f","tid":2264670,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":15,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T22:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6477HN8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6477HN8.jpg&h=6d9f6a7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T22:58:22.000Z","msg":"阿彌陀佛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c04f002ba40a86b4274078d61bbebd8ebc05be1","tid":2264670,"uid":356254,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T23:02:49.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈"},{"pid":"d448bdb36173b858511380274a36f580fcf3e04e","tid":2264670,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3e44626cccbf61fb6c641b8381d140c85e7faa9f","tid":2264670,"uid":347001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":15,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T22:55:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6477HN8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6477HN8.jpg&h=6d9f6a7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T23:02:58.000Z","msg":"阿彌陀佛"},{"pid":"6b69dab3c2d31c280cdb584ad21ac8db896be2e3","ti